@base_url = http://localhost:7071/api

########## Genie hosted local Functions API ##########

### Health check
GET {{base_url}}/health

### Dry skin + dark spots + dewy finish
GET {{base_url}}/products/recommendations?skinType=dry&concerns=dark%20spots&preference=dewy&limit=3

### Oily skin + matte finish under budget
GET {{base_url}}/products/recommendations?skinType=oily&finish=matte&maxPrice=35

### Sensitive-safe routine ideas
GET {{base_url}}/products/recommendations?skinType=sensitive&preference=fragrance-free

### No-results fallback example
GET {{base_url}}/products/recommendations?brand=unknown-brand&finish=matte&maxPrice=10
